name: Coldie 16,565
description:
Portrait of Coldie painted by my
robots with 16,565 brushstrokes. The
robot's AI was trained on images of
Coldie and his avatar taken from his
VRChat gallery on April 10, 2021 -
including one of his self portraits. The
animation in the background is a
visualization of the robot's GANs as it
imagined, re-imagined, painted, and
re-painted his portrait over the
course of 3 days.
